<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>15 estatísticas reveladoras de compras online para 2020</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/pt-pt/blog/category/conversion-rate-optimization" rel="category tag">Conversion Rate Optimization</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-2-1024x437.jpg" alt="Online Shopping Statistics [Wordpress]" class="wp-image-115252" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-2-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-2-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-2-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-2-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-2-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-2-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-2-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-2-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-2-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-2-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-2-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-2-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-2-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-2-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-2-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5fd0950e328ec" class="block-preamble"><p>Foi há <a href="https://money.com/online-shopping-history-anniversary/">25 anos</a> atrás (1994) que a primeira compra online foi documentada.</p>
</div>






<p>Desde então, as compras online cresceram de um conceito novo a uma indústria multibilionária.</p>



<p>Para pôr tudo em perspectiva e ver o estado atual das coisas, eu compilei uma lista com algumas das estatísticas mais reveladoras relacionadas às compras online para 2020.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Estas estatísticas irão lhe mostrar onde a indústria está atualmente, as oportunidades que estão disponíveis, onde ela está indo e o que você pode fazer para ser mais competitivo.</p>



<p>Vamos começar.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5ea160a34171b" class="block-content-upgrade">
