<h2><strong>Índice de conteúdo</strong></h2>



<p><a href="#1">1. As vendas de comércio eletrônico estão previstas para atingir $4,2 bilhões até o fim de 2020 (Statista)</a></p>



<p><a href="#2">2. As vendas de comércio eletrônico estão previstas para atingir $6,5 trilhões até 2023 (Statista)</a></p>



<p><a href="#3">3. Há 2,05 bilhões de compradores online em 2020 (Oberlo)</a></p>



<p><a href="#4">4. 75 por cento das pessoas compram online pelo menos uma vez por mês (Statista)</a></p>



<p><a href="#5">5. 63 por cento das jornadas de compra começam online (pesquisando com o Google)</a></p>



<p><a href="#6">6. Quase metade (49,2 por cento) das vendas de comércio eletrônico foram feitas através de dispositivos móveis em 2020 (Statista)</a></p>



<p><a href="#7">7. Até 2021, 53,9 por cento das vendas de comércio eletrônico serão feitas através de dispositivos móveis (Statista)</a></p>



<p><a href="#8">8. A Amazon representa 47 por cento de todas as vendas de comércio eletrônico nos Estados Unidos em 2020 (Statista)</a></p>



<p><a href="#9">9. A Amazon representará 50 por cento de todas as vendas de comércio eletrônico nos Estados Unidos até 2021 (Statista)</a></p>



<p><a href="#10">10. 80 por cento dos compradores online e 63 por cento dos compradores mobile acham que as novas tecnologias e inovações melhoram sua experiência (Federação Nacional do Varejo)</a></p>



<p><a href="#11">11. Busca e navegação são os elementos de site mais importantes para os compradores online (Statista)</a></p>



<p><a href="#12">12. Ter avaliações e classificações de produto é o segundo elemento mais importante (Statista)</a></p>



<p><a href="#13">13. Ter custos extras é o motivo principal pelo abandono de carrinho (Baymard Institute)</a></p>



<p><a href="#14">14. Forçar o comprador a criar uma conta é o segundo motivo principal pelo abandono de carrinho (Baymard Institute)</a></p>



<p><a href="#15">15. O retargeting dos visitantes do site faz com que tenham uma probabilidade 43 por cento maior de realizarem uma compra (PR Newswire)</a></p>



<h2 id="1">1. As vendas de comércio eletrônico estão previstas para atingir $4,2 bilhões até o fim de 2020 (Statista)</h2>



<p>Houve um crescimento considerável na indústria de comércio eletrônico nos anos recentes. Em 2014, o número total de vendas atingiu apenas <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/379046/worldwide-retail-e-commerce-sales/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">$1,3 trilhões</a>. </p>



<p>Mas esse número mais do que triplicou em 2020 para $4,2 trilhões e é previsto que continue crescendo enquanto estamos nos preparando para a década de 2020.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="790" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-1-1024x790.png" alt="1 Retail e-commerce" class="wp-image-115166" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-1-1024x790.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-1-300x231.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-1-768x593.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-1-1536x1185.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-1-380x293.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-1-600x463.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-1-760x586.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-1-1440x1111.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-1-45x35.png 45w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-1-65x50.png 65w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-1-635x490.png 635w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-1-220x170.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-1-385x297.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-1.png 1664w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<h2 id="2">2. As vendas de comércio eletrônico estão previstas para atingir $6,5 trilhões até 2023 (Statista)</h2>



<p>De fato, os especialistas fizeram projeções anuais de lucro que atingem até <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/379046/worldwide-retail-e-commerce-sales/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">$6,5 trilhões</a> em apenas três anos. </p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="805" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-1-1024x805.png" alt="2 Retail Worldwide" class="wp-image-115168" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-1-1024x805.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-1-300x236.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-1-768x604.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-1-1536x1208.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-1-380x299.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-1-600x472.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-1-760x598.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-1-1440x1132.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-1-45x35.png 45w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-1-64x50.png 64w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-1-623x490.png 623w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-1-220x173.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-1-385x303.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-1.png 1638w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Se esta tendência manter sua trajetória, as vendas de comércio eletrônico poderiam potencialmente atingir $8 trilhões por ano até 2025.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Isto é uma ótima notícia para as marcas digitais e mostra quantas oportunidades estão disponíveis.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Embora o nível de competição certamente aumentará, o lucro também.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Sendo assim, agora é a hora perfeita para subir a bordo.&nbsp;</p>



<h2 id="3">3. Há 2,05 bilhões de compradores online em 2020 (Oberlo)</h2>



<p>Em 2020, há aproximadamente <a href="https://www.worldometers.info/world-population/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">7,8 bilhões</a> de pessoas no mundo. Sendo que quase um quarto delas (<a href="https://www.oberlo.com/statistics/how-many-people-shop-online" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">26,28 por cento</a>) são compradores online. </p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="524" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-1-1024x524.png" alt="3 Oberlo" class="wp-image-115170" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-1-1024x524.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-1-300x153.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-1-768x393.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-1-1536x785.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-1-380x194.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-1-600x307.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-1-760x389.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-1-1440x736.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-1-68x35.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-1-98x50.png 98w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-1-740x378.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-1-220x113.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-1-385x197.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-1.png 1760w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Como você pode ver, houve um aumento considerável no número de compradores online com o passar dos anos, que saltaram de 1,32 bilhões em 2014 a 2,05 bilhões em 2020.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Já que cada vez mais pessoas estão comprando digitalmente, isso quer dizer que as marcas de comércio eletrônico têm a chance de alcançar um público imenso.&nbsp;</p>



<h2 id="4">4. 75 por cento das pessoas compram online pelo menos uma vez por mês (Statista)</h2>



<p>Também vale mencionar que a grande maioria das pessoas que compram online fazem isso com frequência.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Pesquisas da <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/664770/online-shopping-frequency-worldwide/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Statista</a> descobriram que:</p>



<ul><li>20 por cento compram online uma vez por semana</li><li>24 por cento compram online uma vez a cada duas semanas</li><li>31 por cento compram online uma vez por mês</li></ul>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="718" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-1-1024x718.png" alt="4 Additional Information" class="wp-image-115172" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-1-1024x718.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-1-300x210.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-1-768x539.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-1-1536x1077.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-1-380x267.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-1-600x421.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-1-760x533.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-1-1440x1010.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-1-50x35.png 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-1-71x50.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-1-699x490.png 699w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-1-220x154.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-1-385x270.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-1.png 1628w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Em comparação, um número bem menor (15 por cento) compra de 3 a 4 vezes por trimestre, e apenas 10 por cento compra uma vez a cada três meses.&nbsp;</p>



<p>O ponto onde queremos chegar é que as compras online estão se tornando a norma, e há grandes oportunidades para adquirir clientes fiéis que vão comprar com você várias e várias vezes.&nbsp;</p>



<h2 id="5">5. 63 por cento das jornadas de compra começam online (pesquisando com o Google)</h2>



<p>Uma das estatísticas de compras online mais interessantes é que mais de seis entre dez vezes, as jornadas de compra começam online. (<a href="https://www.thinkwithgoogle.com/feature/path-to-purchase-search-behavior/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Fonte</a>.)</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="917" height="1024" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-1-917x1024.png" alt="5 Percentage Circle" class="wp-image-115174" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-1-917x1024.png 917w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-1-269x300.png 269w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-1-768x857.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-1-380x424.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-1-600x670.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-1-760x848.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-1-31x35.png 31w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-1-45x50.png 45w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-1-439x490.png 439w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-1-220x246.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-1-385x430.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-1.png 1014w" sizes="(max-width: 917px) 100vw, 917px" /></figure></div>



<p><em>“63% das ocasiões de compra começam online.”</em></p>



<p>Independentemente se uma pessoa acaba comprando em uma loja de comércio eletrônico ou em uma loja física, grande parte da pesquisa inicial começa em um cenário digital.</p>



<p>“É por isso que é crucial para as marcas terem uma forte presença online,” explica o escritor de comércio eletrônico e dropshipping (envio direto) <a href="https://www.oberlo.com/blog/online-shopping-statistics" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Maryam Moshin</a>. </p>



<p>“Ao melhorar a experiência do cliente desde o primeiro passo, os negócios têm uma chance maior de fazerem com que os clientes comprem em suas lojas.”</p>



<p>Sendo assim, é inteligente investir em estratégias de marketing digital como SEO (otimização para motores de busca) e nas redes sociais.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Marcas que fazem isso geram um maior volume de leads e criam valor da marca que pode valer a pena quando os compradores estão decidindo com quem realizar uma compra.</p>



<p>Por exemplo, a empresa de esfoliação corporal <a href="https://www.frankbody.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Frank Body</a> atualmente possui 745 mil seguidores no Instagram—um fator extremamente importante para a exposição e o sucesso de sua marca.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="461" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-1-1024x461.png" alt="6 Frank Body" class="wp-image-115176" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-1-1024x461.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-1-300x135.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-1-768x346.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-1-1536x692.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-1-380x171.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-1-600x270.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-1-760x342.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-1-1440x648.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-1-78x35.png 78w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-1-111x50.png 111w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-1-740x333.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-1-220x99.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-1-385x173.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-1.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/frank_bod/?hl=en"></a></p>



<h2 id="6">6. Quase metade (49,2 por cento) das vendas de comércio eletrônico foram feitas através de dispositivos móveis em 2020 (Statista)</h2>



<p>Que os compradores online realizam compras através dos dispositivos móveis não é nenhuma novidade. Mas é um aumento de quase <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/249863/us-mobile-retail-commerce-sales-as-percentage-of-e-commerce-sales/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">15 por cento</a> nos quatro anos recentes.</p>



<p>Em 2017, apenas 34,5 por cento das vendas de comércio eletrônico vinham de dispositivos móveis, mas esse número aumentou quase para 50 por cento em 2020.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="703" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-1-1024x703.png" alt="7 Column four" class="wp-image-115180" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-1-1024x703.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-1-300x206.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-1-768x527.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-1-1536x1054.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-1-380x261.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-1-600x412.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-1-760x522.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-1-1440x989.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-1-51x35.png 51w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-1-73x50.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-1-714x490.png 714w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-1-220x151.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-1-385x264.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-1.png 1646w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<h2 id="7">7. Até 2021, 53,9 por cento das vendas de comércio eletrônico serão feitas através de dispositivos móveis (Statista)</h2>



<p>E 2021 deve marcar o ponto crítico oficial onde mais vendas serão feitas através de dispositivos móveis do que através de computadores de mesa e de laptops. (<a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/249863/us-mobile-retail-commerce-sales-as-percentage-of-e-commerce-sales/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Fonte</a>.)</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="713" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-1-1024x713.png" alt="8 Column five" class="wp-image-115182" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-1-1024x713.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-1-300x209.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-1-768x535.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-1-1536x1070.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-1-380x265.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-1-600x418.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-1-760x529.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-1-1440x1003.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-1-50x35.png 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-1-72x50.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-1-703x490.png 703w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-1-220x153.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-1-385x268.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-1.png 1628w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Isto mostra a importância de otimizar o seu site para mobile e oferecer a este segmento de visitantes uma experiência de compra simples.&nbsp;</p>



<h2 id="8">8. A Amazon representa 47 por cento de todas as vendas de comércio eletrônico nos Estados Unidos em 2020 (Statista)</h2>



<p>Eu talvez nem preciso mencionar que a Amazon é uma potência de comércio eletrônico que possui uma porcentagem imensa de participação no mercado.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Mas seu poder aumentou consideravelmente nos anos recentes, onde ela saltou de <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/788109/amazon-retail-market-share-usa/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">34 por cento</a> das vendas de comércio eletrônico nos Estados Unidos em 2016 para 47 por cento em 2020. </p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="722" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-1-1024x722.png" alt="9 column four" class="wp-image-115184" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-1-1024x722.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-1-300x211.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-1-768x541.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-1-1536x1083.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-1-380x268.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-1-600x423.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-1-760x536.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-1-1440x1015.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-1-50x35.png 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-1-71x50.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-1-695x490.png 695w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-1-220x155.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-1-385x271.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-1.png 1620w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<h2 id="9">9. A Amazon representará 50 por cento de todas as vendas de comércio eletrônico nos Estados Unidos até 2021 (Statista)</h2>



<p>E até 2021, é projetado que a Amazon alcance oficialmente metade de todas as vendas de comércio eletrônico nos Estados Unidos. (<a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/788109/amazon-retail-market-share-usa/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Fonte</a>.)</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="710" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-1-1024x710.png" alt="10 column 5" class="wp-image-115188" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-1-1024x710.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-1-300x208.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-1-768x532.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-1-1536x1065.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-1-380x263.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-1-600x416.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-1-760x527.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-1-1440x998.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-1-50x35.png 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-1-72x50.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-1-707x490.png 707w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-1-220x153.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-1-385x267.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-1.png 1624w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Embora a Amazon tenha recebido um nível considerável de escrutínio e crítica pública recentemente, é impossível negar sua presença nas compras online.</p>



<p>Ela aparentemente possui um pouco de tudo—dos livros até os eletrônicos até os mantimentos até o streaming de música. Não estou dizendo isso para assustar ou desencorajar as pequenas marcas de comércio eletrônico.</p>



<p>Mas isso é absolutamente algo que você deve levar em conta, e é vital criar uma estratégia realística que lhe permita competir com a Amazon.</p>



<h2 id="10">10. 80 por cento dos compradores online e 63 por cento dos compradores mobile acham que as novas tecnologias e inovações melhoram sua experiência (Federação Nacional do Varejo)</h2>



<p>Considerando que a própria base das compras online está enraizada em tecnologias de ponta, não deve surpreender a ninguém que esses compradores são fãs de novas tecnologias e inovações. (<a href="https://nrf.com/research/consumer-view-summer-2019" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Fonte</a>.)</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="457" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-1-1024x457.png" alt="11 percent circles" class="wp-image-115190" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-1-1024x457.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-1-300x134.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-1-768x343.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-1-1536x686.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-1-380x170.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-1-600x268.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-1-760x339.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-1-1440x643.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-1-78x35.png 78w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-1-112x50.png 112w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-1-740x330.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-1-220x98.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-1-385x172.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-1.png 1904w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://towardsdatascience.com/top-12-ways-ai-is-revolutionizing-the-online-shopping-ecommerce-trends-9c3e98ef519c" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Sophia Martin</a>, fã de tecnologia e escritora de conteúdo da Xicom.biz, oferece alguns exemplos como:</p>



<ul><li>Inteligência artificial para oferecer suporte ao cliente 24 horas por dia</li><li>Robôs de chat para oferecer soluções imediatas a praticamente qualquer problema que os compradores possam ter</li><li>Aprendizado de máquina para enviar mensagens personalizadas</li><li>Recomendações de produtos com base em histórico de compras, preferências, localização, entre outros</li></ul>



<p>Aqui vai um exemplo da <a href="https://us.pandora.net/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Pandora</a>, uma empresa de jóias dinamarquesa, usando as recomendações de produtos para ajudar os compradores a descobrirem outros produtos dos quais podem estar interessados. </p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="534" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-1-1024x534.jpg" alt="12 Pandora" class="wp-image-115193" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-1-1024x534.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-1-300x157.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-1-768x401.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-1-380x198.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-1-600x313.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-1-760x396.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-1-67x35.jpg 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-1-96x50.jpg 96w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-1-740x386.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-1-220x115.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-1-385x201.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>E isso é apenas a ponta do iceberg. Tecnologias como essa estão rapidamente avançando e evoluindo a todo instante.</p>



<p>Ficar atualizado nos novos acontecimentos e fazer experimentos contínuos pode ajudar a sua marca de comércio eletrônico a entregar uma experiência de cliente muito melhor e a manter a sua concorrência.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Portanto, é absolutamente algo que você deveria aceitar.&nbsp;</p>



<h2 id="11">11. Busca e navegação são os elementos de site mais importantes para os compradores online (Statista)</h2>



<p>Dados recentes revelaram que facilitar a descoberta de produtos através de uma busca e navegação simples era o atributo mais importante para a experiência de compra online de <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/973413/most-important-attributes-online-shopping-shoppers-usa/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">61 por cento</a> dos compradores. </p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="727" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-1-1024x727.png" alt="13 vertical stat" class="wp-image-115194" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-1-1024x727.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-1-300x213.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-1-768x545.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-1-1536x1091.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-1-380x270.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-1-600x426.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-1-760x540.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-1-1440x1022.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-1-49x35.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-1-70x50.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-1-690x490.png 690w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-1-220x156.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-1-385x273.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-1.png 1614w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>E isso faz todo sentido. Afinal de contas, quem quer ter dificuldades para encontrar o que estão procurando?</p>



<p>É por isso que você deve priorizar a busca e a navegação, além de se esforçar constantemente para fazer melhorias contínuas, mesmo se forem apenas mínimas.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Um bom exemplo de uma marca com uma navegação ultra simples é a empresa de calçados <a href="https://www.rollienation.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Rollie Nation</a>.</p>



<p>Imediatamente após visitarem o seu site, os compradores podem encontrar um menu de navegação simples e direto.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="497" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-1-1024x497.png" alt="14 Aura Bar" class="wp-image-115198" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-1-1024x497.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-1-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-1-768x373.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-1-1536x746.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-1-380x185.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-1-600x291.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-1-760x369.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-1-1440x699.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-1-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-1-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-1-740x359.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-1-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-1-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-1.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Com um rápido clique de mouse em uma de suas categorias, eles podem refinar sua busca.</p>



