										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>Faça recomendações de produtos melhores com estas 13 boas práticas</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/pt-pt/blog/category/conversion-rate-optimization" rel="category tag">Conversion Rate Optimization</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Product-Recommendations-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg" alt="Product Recommendations" class="wp-image-105848" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Product-Recommendations-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Product-Recommendations-Wordpress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Product-Recommendations-Wordpress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Product-Recommendations-Wordpress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Product-Recommendations-Wordpress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Product-Recommendations-Wordpress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Product-Recommendations-Wordpress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Product-Recommendations-Wordpress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Product-Recommendations-Wordpress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Product-Recommendations-Wordpress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Product-Recommendations-Wordpress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Product-Recommendations-Wordpress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Product-Recommendations-Wordpress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Product-Recommendations-Wordpress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Product-Recommendations-Wordpress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5ea007bda1105" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Hoje em dia, os consumidores são bombardeados todos os dias com dezenas de anúncios e mensagens promocionais.</span></p>
</div>






<p>Mesmo assim, as empresas que conseguem oferecer uma experiência de compra personalizada estão conseguindo aumentar suas vendas.</p>



<p>De fato, <a href="https://www.evergage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Evergage-2018-Trends-in-Personalization-Survey.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">uma pesquisa da Evergage</a> descobriu que 45% dos consumidores apresentam uma maior probabilidade de comprar e 56% apresentam uma maior probabilidade de retornar em sites que oferecem recomendações de produtos personalizadas.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Além disso, um <a href="http://insight.venturebeat.com/state-of-marketing-technology-hyper-personalization" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">estudo de 2015, pela VentureBeat</a>, descobriu que 75% dos “nativos digitais” esperam dos sites de e-commerce que ofereçam uma experiência de compra personalizada.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Como é de se esperar.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Você preferiria receber recomendações e upsells com base no seu histórico de compras, ou promoções de produtos aleatórios por email? A resposta é óbvia para a maioria das pessoas.</p>



<p>Clientes adoram recomendações de produtos personalizadas com base em seus interesses.</p>



<p>Por exemplo: Quando você está sentir indeciso sobre um produto, certamente verifica seções como &#8220;Você poderá gostar&#8221; ou &#8220;Itens semelhantes&#8221;.</p>



<p>É fácil pensar nas recomendações de produtos como um simples grupo de itens semelhantes. Mas é importante executá-las de maneira inteligente para aumentar as conversões.</p>



<p>Como é possível melhorar suas recomendações de produtos? Como você pode usá-las para aumentar as vendas? Mostraremos diversas estratégias para que você obtenha melhores resultados com as suas recomendações de produto.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5ea0080da1106" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle">RECURSOS GRATUITOS</p>
        <h2 class="text-title">Quer Mais Táticas de Recomendação de Produtos?</h2>
        <div class="text-content"><p>Acesse nosso recurso exclusivo chamado “9 Formas Testadas e Aprovadas de Obter Melhores Recomendações de Produtos” e aprenda como ajudar os visitantes do seu site a fazer melhores decisões de compra.</p>
</div>
                    <a onClick="SleekNote.triggerOnclick('00c91b9b-1dbc-48da-8d77-1dd2cfc8355b');" href="javascript:void(0);" class="text-link" title="Baixe Nosso Recurso Agora Mesmo →">Baixe Nosso Recurso Agora Mesmo →</a>
            </div>
    <div class="image">
        <img src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Grow-Your-Email-List@2x-1.png" title="Quer Mais Táticas de Recomendação de Produtos?">    </div>
</div>


<h2><strong>Táticas de recomendação de produtos Product capazes de aumentar a taxa de conversão</strong></h2>



<h3><strong>1. Utilize imagens boas dos produtos</strong></h3>



<p>Como fazer as pessoas verificarem a sua seção de itens recomendados? Obviamente, você precisa de <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-photography" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">ter boas fotos dos produtos</a>.&nbsp;</p>



<p>As recomendações da <a href="https://www.katespade.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Kate Spade</a> apresentam fotos de altíssima qualidade. Além disso, quando você passa o cursor sobre uma bolsa, o site mostra o uma modelo utilizando o produto.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="403" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-1024x403.png" alt="If You Like This You_ll Love" class="wp-image-92173" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-1024x403.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-300x118.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-768x302.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-1536x605.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-380x150.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-600x236.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-760x299.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-1440x567.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-89x35.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-127x50.png 127w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-740x291.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-220x87.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-385x152.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Isso torna mais fácil para as pessoas imaginarem como vai ficar se comprarem para elas.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="419" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-2-1024x419.png" alt="If You Like This You_ll Love 2" class="wp-image-92169" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-2-1024x419.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-2-300x123.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-2-768x314.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-2-1536x629.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-2-380x155.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-2-600x246.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-2-760x311.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-2-1440x589.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-2-86x35.png 86w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-2-122x50.png 122w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-2-740x303.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-2-220x90.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-2-385x158.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/If-You-Like-This-You_ll-Love-2.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>É uma estratégia simples, mas que ajuda a atrair o interesse do cliente.&nbsp;</p>



<h3><strong>2. Faça boas recomendações</strong></h3>



<p>Existem diferentes tipos de recomendações de produtos.</p>



<p>Você pode criar recomendações baseadas nos itens mais populares, itens semelhantes e assim por diante. Mas você também deve considerar fazer recomendações personalizadas com base nas preferências individuais e dados demográfico dos visitantes.</p>



<p>Com mecanismos de recomendação ou soluções SaaS, é possível identificar padrões e histórico de compras, comportamento, e listas de desejos dos consumidores. Você pode, então, apresentar recomendações feitas sob medida para cada comprador.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="245" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-2-1024x245.png" alt="Customers Who Bought This Item Also Bought 2" class="wp-image-92153" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-2-1024x245.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-2-300x72.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-2-768x184.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-2-1536x367.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-2-380x91.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-2-600x143.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-2-760x182.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-2-1440x344.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-2-146x35.png 146w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-2-209x50.png 209w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-2-740x177.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-2-220x53.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-2-385x92.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-2.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Se você puder obter dados de redes sociais, também pode fazer <a href="http://evergage.com/products/tribes/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">recomendações “aumentadas socialmente”</a>.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Isto te ajudará a descobrir o que os compradores estão pesquisando, comprando e fazendo reviews. Então, você pode utilizar essas informações para identificar e criar as personas e grupos sociais chave. Assim, você poderá oferecer recomendações inteligentes e relevantes para os compradores, aumentando o valor médio dos pedidos.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="588" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Viewed-This-Item-Also-Viewed-These-Products-1024x588.png" alt="Customers Who Viewed This Item Also Viewed These Products" class="wp-image-92161" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Viewed-This-Item-Also-Viewed-These-Products-1024x588.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Viewed-This-Item-Also-Viewed-These-Products-300x172.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Viewed-This-Item-Also-Viewed-These-Products-768x441.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Viewed-This-Item-Also-Viewed-These-Products-380x218.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Viewed-This-Item-Also-Viewed-These-Products-600x344.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Viewed-This-Item-Also-Viewed-These-Products-760x436.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Viewed-This-Item-Also-Viewed-These-Products-61x35.png 61w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Viewed-This-Item-Also-Viewed-These-Products-87x50.png 87w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Viewed-This-Item-Also-Viewed-These-Products-740x425.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Viewed-This-Item-Also-Viewed-These-Products-220x126.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Viewed-This-Item-Also-Viewed-These-Products-385x221.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Viewed-This-Item-Also-Viewed-These-Products.png 1432w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Fonte: <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://woocommerce.com/products/recommendation-engine/" target="_blank">WooCommerce</a></em></p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<p>Uma boa dica é fornecer estas recomendações por email.&nbsp;</p>



<p>A <a href="http://smartmail.io/resources/how-to-use-personalized-product-recommendations-in-email-to-increase-conversions-by-15-or-more/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">SmartMail relata</a> que sugestões de produtos enviadas por email aumentam a taxa de cliques (CTR &#8211; <em>click-through rate</em>) em incríveis 300%, ou mais. Isto representa mais chances de conversão e mais tráfego para o seu site</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="769" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-Just-for-You-1024x769.png" alt="Recommended Just for You" class="wp-image-92209" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-Just-for-You-1024x769.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-Just-for-You-300x225.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-Just-for-You-768x577.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-Just-for-You-1536x1154.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-Just-for-You-380x286.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-Just-for-You-600x451.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-Just-for-You-760x571.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-Just-for-You-1440x1082.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-Just-for-You-47x35.png 47w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-Just-for-You-67x50.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-Just-for-You-652x490.png 652w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-Just-for-You-220x165.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-Just-for-You-385x289.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-Just-for-You.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Fonte: <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.remarkety.com/product-recommendations-the-key-to-cross-sales-and-up-sales-2" target="_blank">Remarkety</a></em></p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<p>Naturalmente, para que isso dê certo, você não pode recomendar os itens aleatoriamente. Suas sugestões de produto e conteúdos das suas campanhas de email devem ser baseados em dados e segmentação da base de usuários. Em seguida, personalize os emails para cada grupo de consumidores.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Outra boa ideia é incluir recomendações nos <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/abandoned-cart-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">emails de carrinho abandonado</a>. Assim, você pode convencer os usuários a voltarem e comprarem algo da sua loja.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="663" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Have-Great-Taste-663x1024.png" alt="You Have Great Taste" class="wp-image-92253" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Have-Great-Taste-663x1024.png 663w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Have-Great-Taste-194x300.png 194w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Have-Great-Taste-768x1187.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Have-Great-Taste-994x1536.png 994w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Have-Great-Taste-380x587.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Have-Great-Taste-600x927.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Have-Great-Taste-760x1174.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Have-Great-Taste-23x35.png 23w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Have-Great-Taste-32x50.png 32w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Have-Great-Taste-317x490.png 317w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Have-Great-Taste-220x340.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Have-Great-Taste-385x595.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Have-Great-Taste.png 1038w" sizes="(max-width: 663px) 100vw, 663px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Fonte: <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.barilliance.com/cart-abandonment-email-best-practices-samples-part-2/" target="_blank">Barilliance</a></em></p>



<h2><strong>Use tipos de recomendação com alta taxa de engajamento</strong></h2>



<p>Existem diferentes tipos de recomendação de produto, mas qual você deveria utilizar?&nbsp;</p>



<p>Segundo um estudo da Barilliance, os tipos de recomendação com mairo engajamento incluem:&nbsp;</p>



<h3><strong>3. O que os clientes compraram</strong></h3>



<p>“O que os clientes compraram” é um tipo básico de recomendação que apresenta os produtos mais populares de uma loja online.</p>



<p>A popularidade frequentemente leva em conta os itens mais vendidos, mas outros sistemas de recomendação também consideram visualizações, comprar, tempo gasto na página, cliques, quantas vezes foi adicionado ao carrinho, etc. <strong>Uma boa dica é selecionar as métricas que melhor representem a popularidade dos seus produtos entre os visitantes.</strong>&nbsp;</p>



<p>Este tipo de recomendação pode aumentar as vendas de forma efetiva devido ao Princípio de Pareto, que diz que&nbsp; <a href="http://www.smartinsights.com/marketing-planning/marketing-models/paretos-8020-rule-marketing/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">80% das vendas vêm de 20% dos produtos</a>.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="987" height="405" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shop-Our-Bestsellers.png" alt="Shop Our Bestsellers" class="wp-image-92241" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shop-Our-Bestsellers.png 987w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shop-Our-Bestsellers-300x123.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shop-Our-Bestsellers-768x315.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shop-Our-Bestsellers-380x156.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shop-Our-Bestsellers-600x246.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shop-Our-Bestsellers-760x312.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shop-Our-Bestsellers-85x35.png 85w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shop-Our-Bestsellers-122x50.png 122w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shop-Our-Bestsellers-740x304.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shop-Our-Bestsellers-220x90.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shop-Our-Bestsellers-385x158.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 987px) 100vw, 987px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Fonte: <a href="https://magemail.co/blog/product-recommendations/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Magemail</a></em></p>



<h3><strong>4. Clientes também visualizaram</strong></h3>



<p>A filtragem colaborativa, ou recomendação de &#8220;clientes também visualizaram&#8221; funciona coletando dados, interesses ou preferências de muitos usuários e pesando com que frequência esses itens se encontraram presentes juntos no histórico de compras ou navegação.</p>



<p>Os itens exibidos assim são personalizados para todos os usuários.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="247" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-1024x247.png" alt="Customers Who Bought This Item Also Bought" class="wp-image-92157" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-1024x247.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-300x72.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-768x185.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-1536x370.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-380x92.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-600x145.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-760x183.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-1440x347.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-145x35.png 145w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-207x50.png 207w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-740x178.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-220x53.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought-385x93.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customers-Who-Bought-This-Item-Also-Bought.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Você também pode sugerir acessórios comprados juntos com frequência. Por exemplo, se você vender um smartfone Samsung, pode incluir acessórios para celular nas recomendações.&nbsp;</p>



<h3><strong>5. Recomendações baseadas no histórico de buscas do Google</strong></h3>



<p>Este tipo de recomendação exibe produtos baseados no histórico de buscas e compras.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="218" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Inspired-by-Your-Browsing-History-1024x218.png" alt="Inspired by Your Browsing History" class="wp-image-92177" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Inspired-by-Your-Browsing-History-1024x218.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Inspired-by-Your-Browsing-History-300x64.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Inspired-by-Your-Browsing-History-768x163.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Inspired-by-Your-Browsing-History-1536x327.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Inspired-by-Your-Browsing-History-380x81.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Inspired-by-Your-Browsing-History-600x128.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Inspired-by-Your-Browsing-History-760x162.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Inspired-by-Your-Browsing-History-1440x306.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Inspired-by-Your-Browsing-History-165x35.png 165w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Inspired-by-Your-Browsing-History-235x50.png 235w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Inspired-by-Your-Browsing-History-740x157.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Inspired-by-Your-Browsing-History-220x47.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Inspired-by-Your-Browsing-History-385x82.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Inspired-by-Your-Browsing-History.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Ele envolve uma quantidade significativa de dados comportamentais dos usuários, que nem sempre está disponível para novos clientes.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Por esse motivo, e-commerces frequentemente possuem um “plano B” ao implementar este tipo de recomendação, onde o sistema fornecerá recomendações mais gerais baseadas em produtos populares ou semelhantes para usuários cujos dados são insuficientes.&nbsp;</p>



<h3><strong>6. Você poderá gostar</strong></h3>



<p>A recomendação do tipo “Você poderá gostar” geralmente sugere produtos semelhantes ao que o usuário está visualizando no momento.&nbsp;</p>



<p>A similaridade pode ser baseada em diferentes métricas. Algumas ferramentas de recomendação avançadas filtram meta-dados (descrições, tags, nome do produto, etc) baseados na similaridade, também podendo levar em conta a categoria, cor, marca, etc.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="689" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Might-Also-Like-1024x689.png" alt="You Might Also Like" class="wp-image-92257" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Might-Also-Like-1024x689.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Might-Also-Like-300x202.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Might-Also-Like-768x517.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Might-Also-Like-1536x1034.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Might-Also-Like-380x256.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Might-Also-Like-600x404.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Might-Also-Like-760x512.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Might-Also-Like-1440x969.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Might-Also-Like-52x35.png 52w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Might-Also-Like-74x50.png 74w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Might-Also-Like-728x490.png 728w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Might-Also-Like-220x148.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Might-Also-Like-385x259.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/You-Might-Also-Like.png 1570w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Fonte: <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://conversio.com/features/recommendations/" target="_blank">Conversio</a></em></p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<p>A Amazon utiliza uma “filtragem colaborativa item-a-item” que calcula a similaridade baseada na avaliação das pessoas para os itens em questão.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



<h3><strong>7. Mais vendidos por categoria</strong></h3>



<p>Você pode fazer os clientes acessarem suas diferentes páginas de categoria recomendando os produtos mais populares ou mais vendidos de cada uma delas.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="824" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/See-More-Bestsellers-In-Toys-_-Games-1024x824.png" alt="See More Bestsellers In Toys _ Games" class="wp-image-92237" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/See-More-Bestsellers-In-Toys-_-Games-1024x824.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/See-More-Bestsellers-In-Toys-_-Games-300x241.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/See-More-Bestsellers-In-Toys-_-Games-768x618.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/See-More-Bestsellers-In-Toys-_-Games-1536x1236.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/See-More-Bestsellers-In-Toys-_-Games-380x306.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/See-More-Bestsellers-In-Toys-_-Games-600x483.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/See-More-Bestsellers-In-Toys-_-Games-760x611.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/See-More-Bestsellers-In-Toys-_-Games-1440x1159.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/See-More-Bestsellers-In-Toys-_-Games-44x35.png 44w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/See-More-Bestsellers-In-Toys-_-Games-62x50.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/See-More-Bestsellers-In-Toys-_-Games-609x490.png 609w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/See-More-Bestsellers-In-Toys-_-Games-220x177.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/See-More-Bestsellers-In-Toys-_-Games-385x310.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/See-More-Bestsellers-In-Toys-_-Games.png 1576w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Uma boa dica não é rotular os produtos estritamente sob uma categoria, mas usar um sistema que ofereça uma maior diversidade nas recomendações. Por exemplo, produtos que podem ser usados tanto por mulheres adolescentes quanto por mulheres adultas devem pertencer a ambas as categorias.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>Experimente com os títulos</strong></h2>



<p>Recomendar produtos é uma coisa, mas a forma como você apresenta e comunica para os seus clientes os itens recomendados é igualmente importante.</p>



<p>Para persuadir os clientes a verificar suas recomendações, procure experimentar vários títulos para descobrir quais são os mais eficazes em gerar engajamento. Vejamos alguns exemplos:</p>



<p>A <a href="https://sokoglam.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Soko Glam</a> apresenta uma seleção de produtos semelhantes sob o título &#8220;Recomendado para você&#8221;, informando aos clientes que as recomendações foram feitas considerando os seus interesses.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="445" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-1024x445.png" alt="Recommended for You" class="wp-image-92205" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-1024x445.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-300x130.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-768x334.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-1536x668.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-380x165.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-600x261.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-760x330.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-1440x626.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-81x35.png 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-115x50.png 115w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-740x322.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-220x96.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-385x167.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Fonte: <a href="https://sokoglam.com/products/botanic-farm-rice-ferment-first-essence" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Soko Glam</a></em></p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<p>A <a href="https://www.kobo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Kobo</a> utiliza uma abordagem semelhante à da Soko Glam, e apresenta uma seleção de livros similares como “Títulos relacionados” e “Mais deste autor.”</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="809" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Related-Titles-1024x809.png" alt="Related Titles" class="wp-image-92225" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Related-Titles-1024x809.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Related-Titles-300x237.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Related-Titles-768x607.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Related-Titles-1536x1214.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Related-Titles-380x300.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Related-Titles-600x474.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Related-Titles-760x601.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Related-Titles-1440x1138.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Related-Titles-44x35.png 44w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Related-Titles-63x50.png 63w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Related-Titles-620x490.png 620w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Related-Titles-220x174.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Related-Titles-385x304.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Related-Titles.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>A <a href="https://www.missguided.eu/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Missguided</a> utiliza sua voz de marca irreverente ao promover seus produtos. Se você possuir uma voz ou identidade de marca específicos, procure jogar com as palavras e faça testes A / B utilizando diversos títulos.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="361" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/More-Fancy-Things-1024x361.png" alt="More Fancy Things" class="wp-image-92181" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/More-Fancy-Things-1024x361.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/More-Fancy-Things-300x106.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/More-Fancy-Things-768x270.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/More-Fancy-Things-1536x541.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/More-Fancy-Things-380x134.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/More-Fancy-Things-600x211.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/More-Fancy-Things-760x268.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/More-Fancy-Things-1440x507.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/More-Fancy-Things-99x35.png 99w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/More-Fancy-Things-142x50.png 142w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/More-Fancy-Things-740x261.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/More-Fancy-Things-220x77.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/More-Fancy-Things-385x136.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/More-Fancy-Things.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<h3><strong>8. Use cores contrastantes Colors&nbsp;</strong></h3>



<p>A cor é um dos elementos mais importantes no design, e também pode ser usada para realçar as suas recomendações de produtos. Por isso, você deve usar cores contrastantes para que as suas recomendações se destaquem do resto da página.</p>



<p>Aqui está outro exemplo do Soko Glam:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="519" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Relief-Pearlsation-Body-Wash-1024x519.png" alt="Relief Pearlsation Body Wash" class="wp-image-92229" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Relief-Pearlsation-Body-Wash-1024x519.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Relief-Pearlsation-Body-Wash-300x152.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Relief-Pearlsation-Body-Wash-768x390.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Relief-Pearlsation-Body-Wash-1536x779.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Relief-Pearlsation-Body-Wash-380x193.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Relief-Pearlsation-Body-Wash-600x304.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Relief-Pearlsation-Body-Wash-760x386.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Relief-Pearlsation-Body-Wash-1440x730.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Relief-Pearlsation-Body-Wash-69x35.png 69w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Relief-Pearlsation-Body-Wash-99x50.png 99w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Relief-Pearlsation-Body-Wash-740x375.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Relief-Pearlsation-Body-Wash-220x112.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Relief-Pearlsation-Body-Wash-385x195.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Relief-Pearlsation-Body-Wash.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="456" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-2-1024x456.png" alt="Recommended for You 2" class="wp-image-92201" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-2-1024x456.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-2-300x133.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-2-768x342.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-2-1536x683.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-2-380x169.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-2-600x267.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-2-760x338.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-2-1440x641.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-2-79x35.png 79w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-2-112x50.png 112w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-2-740x329.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-2-220x98.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-2-385x171.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Recommended-for-You-2.png 1780w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Na página do produto, o plano de fundo dos produto utiliza cinza e branco, enquanto o plano de fundo da seção de produtos recomendados é uma paleta de azul-verde. Os contraste entre as cores torna a seção mais evidente para os usuários. As cores também são agradáveis e <em>clean</em>, o que combina com o design geral do site.</p>



<h3><strong>9. Utilize CTAs convincentes</strong></h3>



<p>Uma recomendação de produto não está completa sem calls-to-action (CTAs) como &#8220;Adicionar ao carrinho&#8221;, Saiba mais&#8221; e assim por diante. Isso deixa mais fácil para os clientes comprarem os produtos ou visitarem a página do produto para saber mais detalhes.</p>



<p>Uma boa dica é deixar perceptível o botão de call-to-action (CTA) bastante evidente. Ele não precisa ser vermelho brilhante. Basta, por exemplo, realçar as bordas, para destacar o CTA como a <a href="https://www.asos.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">ASOS</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="630" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-The-Look-1024x630.png" alt="Buy The Look" class="wp-image-92149" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-The-Look-1024x630.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-The-Look-300x185.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-The-Look-768x473.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-The-Look-1536x946.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-The-Look-380x234.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-The-Look-600x369.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-The-Look-760x468.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-The-Look-1440x887.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-The-Look-57x35.png 57w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-The-Look-81x50.png 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-The-Look-740x456.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-The-Look-220x135.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-The-Look-385x237.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Buy-The-Look.png 1712w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<h2><strong>Recomendação de produtos em páginas 404</strong></h2>



<p>A página 404 é mais do que uma mera mensagem de erro. Ela pode transformar uma boa experiência de comprar em uma grande decepção, e levar os clientes, desapontados, a deixar o site.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Como você pode transformar uma eventual (e praticamente inevitável) página 404 em uma oportunidade?&nbsp;</p>



<p><a href="http://reflektion.com/where-are-retailers-placing-product-recommendations/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Um estudo mostrou</a> que quase a metade das lojas que oferecem recomendação de produtos as incluem também na página 404.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="600" height="360" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Retailers-Using-Recommendations-by-Page.png" alt="Retailers Using Recommendations by Page" class="wp-image-92233" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Retailers-Using-Recommendations-by-Page.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Retailers-Using-Recommendations-by-Page-300x180.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Retailers-Using-Recommendations-by-Page-380x228.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Retailers-Using-Recommendations-by-Page-58x35.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Retailers-Using-Recommendations-by-Page-83x50.png 83w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Retailers-Using-Recommendations-by-Page-220x132.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Retailers-Using-Recommendations-by-Page-385x231.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></figure></div>



<p>Como você pode fazer isso funcionar? Vejamos alguns exemplos simples.</p>



<p>A página 404 da <a href="https://www.stevemadden.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Steve Madden</a> tem um copy interessante e exibe um conjunto dos principais produtos para fazer com que os clientes retornem ao site.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="1020" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Oh-Hey-This-Is-Akward-1024x1020.png" alt="Oh Hey This Is Akward" class="wp-image-92185" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Oh-Hey-This-Is-Akward-1024x1020.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Oh-Hey-This-Is-Akward-300x300.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Oh-Hey-This-Is-Akward-150x150.png 150w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Oh-Hey-This-Is-Akward-768x765.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Oh-Hey-This-Is-Akward-380x379.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Oh-Hey-This-Is-Akward-600x598.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Oh-Hey-This-Is-Akward-760x757.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Oh-Hey-This-Is-Akward-35x35.png 35w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Oh-Hey-This-Is-Akward-50x50.png 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Oh-Hey-This-Is-Akward-492x490.png 492w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Oh-Hey-This-Is-Akward-220x219.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Oh-Hey-This-Is-Akward-385x384.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Oh-Hey-This-Is-Akward-120x120.png 120w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Oh-Hey-This-Is-Akward.png 1440w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Fonte: <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://amasty.com/blog/best-404-page-examples-in-e-commerce/" target="_blank">Amasty</a></em></p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<p>A <a href="https://www.nike.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Nike</a> utiliza uma abordagem semelhante. Ela possui um copy simples, acompanhado de links para os produtos.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1005" height="636" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Men_s-Products.png" alt="Top Men_s Products" class="wp-image-92245" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Men_s-Products.png 1005w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Men_s-Products-300x190.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Men_s-Products-768x486.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Men_s-Products-380x240.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Men_s-Products-600x380.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Men_s-Products-760x481.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Men_s-Products-55x35.png 55w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Men_s-Products-79x50.png 79w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Men_s-Products-740x468.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Men_s-Products-220x139.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Men_s-Products-385x244.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1005px) 100vw, 1005px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Fonte: <a href="https://www.wpromote.com/blog/digital-marketing/what-makes-a-solid-404-page-with-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Wpromote</a></em></p>



<h3><strong>10. Considere o uso do espaço Above the Fold x Below the Fold</strong></h3>



<p>O conceito de “above the fold” se origina dos jornais, que ficavam dobrados em um suporte ou prateleira nas bancas de jornais. O espaço sobre a dobra (“above the fold”) era a única parte visível para os transeuntes, escondendo o que estava abaixo da dobra (“Below the Fold”). Então, as editoras frequentemente utilizavam <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-headlines" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">imagens e títulos chamativos</a> neste espaço para atrair os leitores.&nbsp;</p>



<p>O mesmo princípio se aplica a websites. Qualquer conteúdo que não esteja imediatamente visível ao se abrir a página ou que o usuário precise “rolar para baixo” para ver é considerado Below the Fold</p>



<p>Mas, como você sabe, a localização importa muito nos sites de e-commerce.</p>



<p>A Barilliance reporta que recomendações Above the Fold são <a href="https://www.barilliance.com/product-recommendations-best-practices/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">1.7x mais efetivas</a> que as below the fold.</p>



<p>Os clientes que estão navegando entre várias páginas de produto frequentemente já decidiram comprar algo antes mesmo de visitar o site. Eles desejam fazer uma compra, mas ainda não têm certeza sobre o item específico que devem comprar. Nesses casos, colocar recomendações Above the Fold é uma questão de conveniência para os compradores.</p>



<p>A <a href="https://www.etsy.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Etsy</a>, por exemplo, posiciona as recomendações discretamente no canto superior direito para que seja mais fácil para os clientes encontrarem itens semelhantes.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="603" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Etsy-Product-Page-1024x603.png" alt="Etsy Product Page" class="wp-image-92165" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Etsy-Product-Page-1024x603.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Etsy-Product-Page-300x177.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Etsy-Product-Page-768x453.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Etsy-Product-Page-1536x905.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Etsy-Product-Page-380x224.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Etsy-Product-Page-600x354.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Etsy-Product-Page-760x448.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Etsy-Product-Page-1440x849.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Etsy-Product-Page-59x35.png 59w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Etsy-Product-Page-85x50.png 85w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Etsy-Product-Page-740x436.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Etsy-Product-Page-220x130.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Etsy-Product-Page-385x227.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Etsy-Product-Page.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<h3><strong>11. Adicione recomendações na página do carrinho</strong></h3>



<p>Outra maneira de utilizar recomendações para aumentar o valor médio da venda é incluí-las na página do carrinho&nbsp;</p>



<p><a href="http://www.nosto.com/blog/6-layers-effective-product-recommendations/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Um estudo descobriu</a> que 25% dos clientes que clicam nessas recomendações acabam comprando.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="800" height="766" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Checkout-Page.jpg" alt="Zalando Checkout Page" class="wp-image-92261" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Checkout-Page.jpg 800w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Checkout-Page-300x287.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Checkout-Page-768x735.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Checkout-Page-380x364.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Checkout-Page-600x575.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Checkout-Page-760x728.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Checkout-Page-37x35.jpg 37w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Checkout-Page-52x50.jpg 52w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Checkout-Page-512x490.jpg 512w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Checkout-Page-220x211.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zalando-Checkout-Page-385x369.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Fonte: <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.brainsins.com/en/blog/shopping-cart-page-recommendation-strategy/2496" target="_blank">BrainSINS</a></em></p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<p>Você também pode oferecer frete grátis como incentivo adicional para comprar o produto.</p>



<p>Por exemplo, se você oferece frete grátis a partir de um determinado valor, pode ajudar os clientes a atingir esse valor oferecendo itens que complementam o que eles estão comprando.</p>



<p>Isso com certeza aumentará os seus lucros.</p>



<h3><strong>12. Use recomendações de produtos nos emails de confirmação de compra</strong></h3>



<p>Um cliente comprou um item na sua loja. Bom trabalho! Mas por que parar por aí? Como estimular compras adicionais pelo mesmo usuário?</p>



<p><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/order-confirmation-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Emails de confirmação de pedido</a> te dão mais uma oportunidade de fazer upsell.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Na verdade, <a href="https://receiptful.com/blog/email-receipts-infographic/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">um estudo mostrou</a> que os e-mails de confirmação de pedidos têm uma taxa de visualização de 70,9%, o que é 4 vezes maior do que a média geral dos emails promocionais. E faz sentido, já que depois de uma compra, quase todo mundo verifica imediatamente o seu email para confirmar que a transação foi bem sucedida.</p>



<p>Veja este exemplo da <a href="https://www.udemy.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Udemy</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="637" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Udemy-Order-Confirmation-637x1024.png" alt="Udemy Order Confirmation" class="wp-image-92249" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Udemy-Order-Confirmation-637x1024.png 637w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Udemy-Order-Confirmation-187x300.png 187w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Udemy-Order-Confirmation-768x1235.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Udemy-Order-Confirmation-380x611.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Udemy-Order-Confirmation-600x965.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Udemy-Order-Confirmation-760x1222.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Udemy-Order-Confirmation-22x35.png 22w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Udemy-Order-Confirmation-31x50.png 31w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Udemy-Order-Confirmation-305x490.png 305w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Udemy-Order-Confirmation-220x354.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Udemy-Order-Confirmation-385x619.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Udemy-Order-Confirmation.png 872w" sizes="(max-width: 637px) 100vw, 637px" /></figure></div>



<p>A Udemy exibe cursos que também foram comprados por outros clientes que adquiriram o mesmo curso. Esta é outra tática simples que pode facilmente estimular o interesse do cliente.</p>



<h3><strong>13. Crie páginas de destino com recomendações personalizadas</strong></h3>



<p>Se um cliente está procurando por bolsas, mas quando visita seu site só encontra itens não relacionados (por exemplo, sapatos, acessórios ou outros itens que você venda), o botão de voltar é uma consequência inevitável.</p>



<p>Então, como você tornar mais rápido e fácil para os clientes encontrarem o que procuram? Como acelerar o processo de compra? Crie páginas de destino personalizadas com produtos relacionados ou semelhantes.</p>



<p>Você pode criar uma página de destino baseadas em termos de pesquisa ou palavras-chave populares relacionadas à sua marca. Por exemplo, se o seu negócio é vender vestidos vermelhos, como a Forever 21, crie uma página de destino que recomende todos os vestidos vermelhos que você vende.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="698" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-1024x698.png" alt="Red Dress" class="wp-image-92217" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-1024x698.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-300x204.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-768x523.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-380x259.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-600x409.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-760x518.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-51x35.png 51w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-73x50.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-719x490.png 719w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-220x150.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-385x262.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress.png 1380w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="634" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-SERP-Results-1024x634.png" alt="Red Dress SERP Results" class="wp-image-92213" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-SERP-Results-1024x634.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-SERP-Results-300x186.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-SERP-Results-768x475.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-SERP-Results-380x235.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-SERP-Results-600x371.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-SERP-Results-760x470.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-SERP-Results-57x35.png 57w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-SERP-Results-81x50.png 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-SERP-Results-740x458.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-SERP-Results-220x136.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-SERP-Results-385x238.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dress-SERP-Results.png 1412w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Isso não só vai aumentar o seu rank de pesquisa para uma palavra-chave relevante, mas também ajudará a atrair clientes provenientes do Google ou outros mecanismos de busca.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="579" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dresses-1024x579.png" alt="Red Dresses" class="wp-image-92221" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dresses-1024x579.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dresses-300x170.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dresses-768x434.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dresses-1536x868.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dresses-380x215.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dresses-600x339.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dresses-760x430.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dresses-1440x814.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dresses-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dresses-88x50.png 88w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dresses-740x418.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dresses-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dresses-385x218.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Red-Dresses.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>


