										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>Como usar marketing psicográfico para gerar um perfil de usuário baseado em dados</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/pt-pt/blog/category/growth-marketing" rel="category tag">Growth Marketing</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="240" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-1024x240.jpg" alt="Psychographic Marketing (WordPress)" class="wp-image-92434" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-1024x240.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-300x70.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-768x180.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-1536x360.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-2048x480.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-380x89.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-600x141.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-760x178.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-1440x338.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-149x35.jpg 149w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-213x50.jpg 213w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-740x173.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-220x52.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Psychographic-Marketing-Wordpress-385x90.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5ea148949c4e1" class="block-preamble"><p><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">“Conhece teu cliente.” </span></i><span style="font-weight: 400;">Esta máxima se aplica para qualquer profissional do marketing, independente do setor, nicho, etc. E não basta saber o “quem”. Você também precisa saber o “quando” e o “porque”.</span></p>
</div>






<p>Para a sua campanha realmente florescer, é essencial conhecer o panorama geral, e saber o que motiva o cliente.</p>



<p>E é aí que o marketing psicográfico entra em cena.</p>


