										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>Como criar emails promocionais com alta taxa de conversão (sem parecer forçado)</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/email-marketing" rel="category tag">Email Marketing</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promotional-Emails-Wordpress-1-1024x437.jpg" alt="Promotional Emails [Wordpress]" class="wp-image-91838" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promotional-Emails-Wordpress-1-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promotional-Emails-Wordpress-1-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promotional-Emails-Wordpress-1-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promotional-Emails-Wordpress-1-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promotional-Emails-Wordpress-1-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promotional-Emails-Wordpress-1-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promotional-Emails-Wordpress-1-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promotional-Emails-Wordpress-1-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promotional-Emails-Wordpress-1-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promotional-Emails-Wordpress-1-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promotional-Emails-Wordpress-1-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promotional-Emails-Wordpress-1-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promotional-Emails-Wordpress-1-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promotional-Emails-Wordpress-1-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promotional-Emails-Wordpress-1-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5e9db051bebc5" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Pense no seguinte cenário: Você é dono de um e-commerce querendo promover um produto. Pode ser um produto novo, uma oferta sazonal ou simplesmente um produto já existente que você deseja divulgar.</span></p>
</div>






<p>Qualquer que seja o caso, emails são uma das formas mais diretas e efetivas de direcionar o tráfego para a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-product-pages" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">página do seu produto</a>.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Estudos revelam que “Os emails possuem um <a href="https://www.emarketer.com/Article/Email-Continues-Deliver-Strong-ROI-Value-Marketers/1014461" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">ROI (retorno de investimento) de 122%</a> — mais de 4 vezes maior que outras formas de marketing como mídias sociais, email direto e pesquisas pagas.”</p>



<p>Mas, como você deve saber, existem muitos fatores envolvidos na criação de um email com alta taxa de conversão, e você precisa seguir uma sequência correta de passos para que eles funcionem.</p>



<p>Você precisa, primeiro, garantir que o email chegue na caixa de entrada dos usuários inscritos, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/email-subject-lines" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">fazê-los abrir o email</a>, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-copywriting" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">seduzi-los com um bom copy</a>, fazê-los clicar no CTA e, finalmente, convencê-los a concluir uma compra.</p>



<p>Neste post, explicarei o processo de forma detalhada e falarei sobre os principais elementos que compõe um email promocional com alta taxa de conversão.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Vamos começar?</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e99680e7de46" class="block-content-upgrade alignleft">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle">RECURSOS GRATUITOS</p>
